Auth-related Worker code lives in `src/index.ts`.

Resend setup note:

- Run `npx wrangler secret put RESEND_API_KEY` from the project root.
- Paste the Resend API key when Wrangler prompts for it.
- This stores the key as a Cloudflare Worker secret for this project; it does not belong in source files or `wrangler.jsonc`.
- If using a Resend subdomain (for example `updates.servewell.net`), set `AUTH_FROM_EMAIL` in `wrangler.jsonc` to that subdomain sender (for example `no-reply@updates.servewell.net`).
- After setting the secret, run `npx wrangler deploy` so the deployed Worker can use it for magic-link email delivery.